This is part 2 of 3

k heres a big one
 - Distance logger ( athletes will b able to log how many miles they ran, wat shoes, wat route, wat type of weather, wat pace etc. ) zelwak told me to add in this feature cause it will b really helpful
 - It will also have a Distance Graph, where it will create a graph from a starting date to end date of how many miles u ran, etc. (U will b able to select the start and end date)
 
 - It will also have reminders, so u will b able to add ur own reminders such as project due tmrw and tell it to remind u at 10 pm and the program will run in the background and wen its 10 pm it will pop up and say u hav a project due etc. 

- Also coach will b able to add reminders from his program tat i will supply him, so he can b like "faraz u need to run 2 miles tmrw at 7 am", and wen i open the program on my computer it will tell me zelwak's message

Your birth on the 2nd day of the month adds a degree of emotion, sensitivity, and intuition to your life. The 2 is a very social number allowing you to make friends easily and quickly.
